  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare two different medications (neostigmine/glycopyrrolate
      and sugammadex) to see if one drug improves patient comfort regarding the return of muscle
      strength after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
